{"tid":1342514,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下次交稅交少4.96%以示不滿！","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T07:24:31.000Z","uid":61861,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7040bad18838c7a69a9d0586d023cc72ba964eae","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:40:03.000Z","msg":"基於今日元朗發生嘅事件，我認為警隊已經失去除暴安良嘅能力。<br />\n<br />\n1. 單係元朗站，報警超過30mins 以上都冇警員到場(受訪現場人士表示)。事實上約6:00pm元朗已經有白衫人集結，約10:00pm已經收到有片白衫人打途經市民！！<br />\n2. 警員到場後，沒有對現場滯留市民提供任何保護就收隊。<br />\n3. 其後元朗及天水圍警署落閘，直至約1:00am先喺各媒體出現。(有錯請指正)<br />\n<br />\n根據政府庫務署2017-2018財政年度的報告，政府總支出379,472,746千元(3794億元)，警務處支出18,785,027千元(187億元)，特首辦支出116,930千元(1.17億元)。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警務處及特首辦佔政府總支出4.96%，既然警察唔做野香港人冇理由養佢地。因此我希望各位下次交稅交少4.96%以示不滿！</span></span></strong><br />\n(警務處佔政府總支出4.93%)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">欠交嘅稅會俾稅局追，後續既行動未諗。請指教！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.try.gov.hk/cinternet/pdc_cbac1718_seacomp18.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.try.gov.hk%2Fcinternet%2Fpdc_cbac1718_seacomp18.pdf&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1AESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=29534ac1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.try.gov.hk/cinternet/pdc_cbac1718_seacomp18.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔知點解何君堯議員(執業大律師)點解會同白衫人士有連繫！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/roy.law3/videos/10220088379464083/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Froy.law3%2Fvideos%2F10220088379464083%2F&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1AESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=329b268c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/roy.law3/videos/10220088379464083/</a><br />\n<br />\n大肚婆都打<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091711245286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fwesterndistrict%2Fpermalink%2F10156091711245286&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1AESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=eba4df97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/westerndistrict/permalink/10156091711245286</a>"},{"pid":"d0cdb249aaaef2fa0eae16ca03bfa71fa7f64480","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d2a57fd2d9f415fda089bdf5ed18d3c2cc790e","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:31:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"aca9dd13e007f5190c775ed813aa6fb35bc70854","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:21:36.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"2df215c7b49cbe93546adedd9320361a3349448d","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:36:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ec5b3f80c87ffbe444b9ce2d136a96d2e0bb506","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:08:45.000Z","msg":"我屌晒你地班連登仔係咪咁鐘意交稅？"},{"pid":"380cd974098cbeaaf137956ef33882c73e19d5a3","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:54:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7e46fc325d3c552e446797093db2d54dd914cb0","tid":1342514,"uid":53780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"仲4.96？<br />\n1蚊都唔交"},{"pid":"fd4575e89df8ba8b4bb43eecfc663c952d8d33c2","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7e46fc325d3c552e446797093db2d54dd914cb0","tid":1342514,"uid":53780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"仲4.96？<br />\n1蚊都唔交"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"不反對"},{"pid":"e58853cb4865087241815babdb26a864f93b9cb9","tid":1342514,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7040bad18838c7a69a9d0586d023cc72ba964eae","tid":1342514,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,